Description: Multi-display Pomodoro timer with screen overlay
 A comprehensive Pomodoro timer application that helps you maintain
 focus during work sessions and enforces breaks with full-screen
 overlays across all connected displays.
 .
 Features:
  * Multi-display support with full-screen overlays
  * Visual countdown timer
  * Desktop notifications
  * Inactivity detection
  * Configurable work/break periods
  * Systemd service integration
  * Cross-desktop compatibility
 .
 This application uses screen overlays instead of system screen locks
 for better compatibility across different desktop environments. 